{{Infobox language |name=Correguaje |nativename=''Ko'reuaju'' |states=[[Colombia]] |region= |ethnicity= |speakers=2,100 |date=2008 |ref=e18 |familycolor=American |fam1=[[Tucanoan languages|Tucanoan]] |iso3=coe |glotto=kore1283 |glottorefname=Koreguaje }}
'''Correguaje''' (Korewaje, Ko'reuaju) is a [[Tucanoan languages|Tucanoan language]] of [[Colombia]].
The language was spoken in the film ''[[Out of the Dark (2014 film)|Out of the Dark]]''.
