The '''National Association of Professors of Hebrew''' (NAPH) is a professional organization for university professors of the [[Hebrew language]] in the United States.<ref name="americanjewishyearbook2015">{{cite book|editor1-last=Dashefsky |editor1-first=Arnold||editor2-last=Sheskin|editor2-first=Ira M.|title=American Jewish Year Book 2015: The Annual Record of the North American Jewish Communities|date=2016|publisher=Springer Publishing|location=New York City|isbn=9783319245034|oclc=917363074|page=618|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=gaqFCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA618&dq=National+Association+of+Professors+of+Hebrew&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi0xYL_mNrNAhWGF5oKHaPzA_0Q6AEILjAF#v=onepage&q=National%20Association%20of%20Professors%20of%20Hebrew&f=false}}</ref> It was established in 1950.<ref name="mintzhebrewinamerica">{{cite book|editor1-last=Mintz|editor1-first=Alan L.|title=Hebrew in America: Perspectives and Prospects|date=1993|publisher=Wayne State University Press|location=Detroit, Michigan|isbn=9780814323519|oclc=25747573|page=180|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=lnYGGqp6qlsC&pg=PA180&dq=National+Association+of+Professors+of+Hebrew&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi0xYL_mNrNAhWGF5oKHaPzA_0Q6AEIRjAJ#v=onepage&q=National%20Association%20of%20Professors%20of%20Hebrew&f=false}}</ref><ref name="aboutus">{{cite web|title=About Us|url=http://www.naphhebrew.org/about-us|website=National Association of Professors of Hebrew|accessdate=July 4, 2016}}</ref>
